THEME

Read this file if you plan to create a theme (see brzdm.theme).

Some basic information regarding the brzdm theme format follows:

Imlib2 is used for image and text display.

A Brzdm theme essentially consists of:
  1. a set of panels with:
  	- a background image (PNG or JPEG) or specification,
  	- an optional text message with font settings,
  	- their placement and properties (see brzdm.theme)

  2. a set of buttons with:
   	- a background image (PNG or JPEG),
  	- an associated command and keystroke,
  	- their placement and properties (see brzdm.theme)

All images are alpha-blended into the main background image.
